Class RhnMockDynaActionForm

  • java.lang.Object
    • DynaActionForm
      • com.redhat.rhn.testing.RhnMockDynaActionForm

  • public class RhnMockDynaActionForm
extends DynaActionForm
    RhnMockDynaActionForm is a mock implementation of a Struts DynaActionForm which allows the user to set expected values during testing.
